{"tid":2058303,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"監警會加國專家：香港警方應勇於認錯　抨擊大規模截查或涉「非法禁錮」","createTime":"2020-06-10T05:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T15:46:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":50,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b4565ecc3dec566cf7d834ae2ae75b66911ac2db","tid":2058303,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/30828/gerry_mcneilly-30828/%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%87%89%E5%8B%87%E6%96%BC%E8%AA%8D%E9%8C%AF-%E6%8A%A8%E6%93%8A%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5%E6%88%96%E6%B6%89%E3%80%8C%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E9%8C%AE%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F30828%2Fgerry_mcneilly-30828%2F%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%258B%2587%25E6%2596%25BC%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%258C%25AF-%25E6%258A%25A8%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E6%2588%25AA%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%25B6%2589%25E3%2580%258C%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%258C%25AE%25E3%2580%258D&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVaxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=7cf90ad9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/30828/gerry_mcneilly-30828/%E7%9B%A3%E8%AD%A6%E6%9C%83%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%9A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%87%89%E5%8B%87%E6%96%BC%E8%AA%8D%E9%8C%AF-%E6%8A%A8%E6%93%8A%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E6%88%AA%E6%9F%A5%E6%88%96%E6%B6%89%E3%80%8C%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E7%A6%81%E9%8C%AE%E3%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n本港監警會早前發表報告，認為警方處理反對逃犯條例修訂運動示威及使用武力並無制度缺失，並提出檢討武力及催淚彈指引。監警會國際專家小組前成員、曾領導加拿大安大略省監察警方投訴組織的Gerry McNeilly接受眾新聞獨家訪問時表示，不會容忍個別警員處理示威期間的行為，又認為警方應勇於承認錯誤，用行動向公眾證明會改革，挽回公眾信心。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;問責必須由警隊最高層開始，由警務處處長承認事件可以做得更好。正如芝加哥市長最近談及問責，不是所有人都做得對，但必須開始做對的事。所以如果我是警務處處長，我會承認我們有犯錯，並且會改正。我們也只能與公眾一同面對及修正這些過錯。&quot;"},{"pid":"e06b902143b936861337a85038221eaa784e851a","tid":2058303,"uid":107577,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:21:18.000Z","msg":"收皮啦收皮啦"},{"pid":"2ac8c9ba67201d7f42062795647c56d5712516a7","tid":2058303,"uid":107577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:21:37.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"d366143ac5806a8efa6e11e0efad8dc9dbbc99ad","tid":2058303,"uid":132587,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wLU10WX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwLU10WX.png&h=35897227&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d8afa88e34603c3447d248f1952b229df967132","tid":2058303,"uid":34755,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:23:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6524ef448b9b21d360a0012724d7fb7fd636cae5","tid":2058303,"uid":335434,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:24:10.000Z","msg":"當年邊個sell成立監狗會海外專家小組呢條橋俾林奠!? 果條友肯定係憎林奠憎到入骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab13675bd194d99b1942a74cf023e6392ceeae0","tid":2058303,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:25:11.000Z","msg":"美國根本做哂示範<br />\n黑警話拉就拉"},{"pid":"d6a4f05ecb7c3d4df81e05b006ea2ae6d6df6b5a","tid":2058303,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644624ef691700915cdb241bbb31a143d4108deb","tid":2058303,"uid":113000,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6524ef448b9b21d360a0012724d7fb7fd636cae5","tid":2058303,"uid":335434,"like":8,"di